[[File:Tom_Seaver_2011.jpg|thumb]]
1988年，背號41號被列入大都會隊退休背號。1992年首度獲得美國棒球名人堂投票資格，並以98.8%，當時史上最高得票率入選，1999年被The Sporting News選為史上百大傑出球員，排名第32<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.baseball-almanac.com/legendary/lisn100.shtml |title=100 Greatest Baseball Players by The Sporting News |accessdate=2015-01-08 |archive-date=2019-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829132658/https://www.baseball-almanac.com/legendary/lisn100.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2008年大都會隊前主場館[[謝亞球場|謝亞球場]]舉行閉幕式，西佛回到現場投出謝亞球場的最後一球。

2011年65岁的西佛转而投身葡萄酒酿造业，建立了自己的Seaver家族葡萄园<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.efoods.com.cn/jl/ShowArticle.asp?ArticleID=63393 |title=棒球天王Tom Seaver推出自酿葡萄酒 |access-date=2015-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115746/http://www.efoods.com.cn/jl/ShowArticle.asp?ArticleID=63393 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

== 健康問題與逝世 ==
2013年，西佛的記憶開始嚴重衰退<ref>{{Cite web|title=NY Mets great and Hall of Fame pitcher Tom Seaver feeling better, winning his battle with Lyme disease|url=https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/mets/madden-tom-nearing-terrific-day-mets-legend-winning-battle-lyme-disease-article-1.1289293|accessdate=2020-09-03|last=Madden|first=Bill|work=nydailynews.com|archive-date=2019-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190706013257/https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/mets/madden-tom-nearing-terrific-day-mets-legend-winning-battle-lyme-disease-article-1.1289293|dead-url=no}}</ref>，好友和作家比爾·馬登在寫書後透露：馬登比對16年和17年訪問西佛時，西佛已在17年完全忘記他的棒球生涯。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Bill Madden on legacy of Seaver - YouTube|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QbkpbT4wNMM|accessdate=2020-11-24|work=www.youtube.com|archive-date=2022-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220110013831/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QbkpbT4wNMM|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年，家人才向外界宣布他患有[[阿茲海默症|阿茲海默症]]，從此不再露面。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hall of Famer Seaver to retire from public life|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/tom-seaver-retires-from-public-life|accessdate=2020-09-03|work=MLB.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819071502/https://www.mlb.com/news/tom-seaver-retires-from-public-life|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年8月31日，西佛因[[失智症|失智症]]、[[莱姆病|萊姆病]]和[[2019冠状病毒病|COVID-19]]併發症，在家中離世，享壽75歲。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tom Seaver, the greatest Met of all time, dies at 75|url=https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/mets/ny-tom-seaver-obituary-20200903-fyusabaogjepzf6uixn6476k5u-story.html|accessdate=2020-09-03|last=Madden|first=Bill|work=nydailynews.com|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903004003/https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/mets/ny-tom-seaver-obituary-20200903-fyusabaogjepzf6uixn6476k5u-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Hall of Fame pitcher Tom Seaver passes away at age 75|url=https://baseballhall.org/discover/hall-of-fame-pitcher-tom-seaver-passes-away|accessdate=2020-09-03|work=Baseball Hall of Fame|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903232555/https://baseballhall.org/discover/hall-of-fame-pitcher-tom-seaver-passes-away|dead-url=no}}</ref>

